Tricky Lacanau Whittles Down Field

A marathon day saw two full rounds of competition in Lacanau, preparing for a big weekend in the French surf city.

Jesse Mendes Wins 3-Star Maui and Sons

The Brazilian surfer took on big barrels to win the Qualification Series event at El Gringo in Arica, Chile.
